Author: truemearoundyou
Text: thank you :( unfortunately the daughter and I are around the same age and she frequently works in my city and we have mutual friends, so I would rather they not know about my ED.

Author: nosoulto_sell
Text: I know the feeling, I am sorry you feel like that :( You said your Dad knows about your ED, maybe he can talk to them and ask them to not mention food or diets etc... ?
